    • Method Detail

      • assignDepartment

        void assignDepartment​(java.lang.String departmentCode)
               throws java.lang.IllegalStateException,
                      java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Assigns this client to a given department

        Preconditions:
        The client may not have already been assigned to a department
        Postconditions:
        The client will be assigned to the given department
        Parameters:
        departmentCode - The department code to assign. May not be empty or null.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - If this client has already been assigned to a department.
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If any argument requirements are breached
